plague-low-protect-1-name = Low defense I
plague-low-protect-1-desc = Clothing begins to protect worse against the disease.

plague-low-protect-2-name = Low defense II
plague-low-protect-2-desc = Clothing begins to protect worse against the disease.

plague-low-protect-3-name = Low defense III
plague-low-protect-3-desc = Clothing begins to protect worse against the disease.

plague-clean-1-name = Cleanliness I
plague-clean-1-desc = Maintaining hygiene becomes less effective for combating the plague.

plague-clean-2-name = Cleanliness II
plague-clean-2-desc = Turns nearly all attempts at maintaining cleanliness to dust. Only a hot bath might save such a patient.

plague-low-sleep-protect-1-name = Beds I
plague-low-sleep-protect-1-desc = Regular beds stop protecting against the disease.

plague-low-sleep-protect-2-name = Beds II
plague-low-sleep-protect-2-desc = Luxurious beds stop protecting against the disease.

plague-immune-break-1-name = Immunity break I
plague-immune-break-1-desc = Allows you to remove immunity from an infected person if it was acquired less than 15 minutes ago.

plague-immune-break-2-name = Immunity break II
plague-immune-break-2-desc = Allows you to remove immunity from an infected person, even if it was acquired more than 15 minutes ago.

plague-contact-spread-1-name = Contact transmission I
plague-contact-spread-1-desc = Infected individuals begin to infect others with a low chance upon physical contact.

plague-contact-spread-2-name = Contact transmission II
plague-contact-spread-2-desc = Infected individuals begin to infect others with a medium chance upon physical contact.

plague-contact-spread-3-name = Contact transmission III
plague-contact-spread-3-desc = Infected individuals begin to infect others with a high chance upon physical contact.

plague-skeleton-spread-name = Plague skeletons
plague-skeleton-spread-desc = Skeletons begin to spread the plague.

plague-animal-spread-1-name = Plague animals I
plague-animal-spread-1-desc = Animals begin to spread the plague.

plague-animal-spread-2-name = Plague animals II
plague-animal-spread-2-desc = Animals begin to spread the plague more effectively.

plague-reroll-cure-name = Cure
plague-reroll-cure-desc = Changes the potion that cures the disease to a different one.

plague-low-bloodletting-eff-1-name = Inconspicuousness I
plague-low-bloodletting-eff-1-desc = Bloodletting becomes less accurate and more often shows false results.

plague-low-bloodletting-eff-2-name = Inconspicuousness II
plague-low-bloodletting-eff-2-desc = Bloodletting becomes even less accurate and shows false results almost as often as correct ones.